OL,3,CJersey Airport placed under 'special
OL,4,Cattention'
OL,6,FJersey Airport is receiving extra
OL,7,Fsurveillance from safety experts
OL,8,Ffollowing a changeover of staff.
OL,10,FThe 'additional regulatory oversight',
OL,11,Falso known as 'special attention',
OL,12,Fcomes from the Office of the Director
OL,13,Fof Civil Aviation - and can be applied
OL,14,Fwhere there are safety concerns,
OL,15,Fcomplex development or significant
OL,16,Foperational changes.
OL,18,FPorts of Jersey say it is due to
OL,19,Fchanges made to the operational
OL,20,Fleadership team.
