OL,3,CJersey Airport placed under 'special
OL,4,Cattention'
OL,6,FITV News understands that seven new
OL,7,Fteam members have been hired. They are
OL,8,Ffrom places like Gatwick and even
OL,9,FDubai Airport.
OL,11,FPorts explained that the move is to
OL,12,F"ensure high safety standards and
OL,13,Fregulatory compliance are maintained,
OL,14,Fwhile new, highly experienced, members
OL,15,Fof the senior operational team
OL,16,Fintegrate into their roles."
OL,18,FMichael Gadd has spent 35 years in the
OL,19,Faviation industry, working with the
OL,20,FCivil Aviation Authority and the
OL,21,FEuropean Aviation Safety Agency.
