OL,6,FHe said: "It's not unreasonable for
OL,7,Fthe regulator to increase the level of
OL,8,Fsurveillance, maybe carry out some
OL,9,Fadditional audits to be satisfied that
OL,10,Fthe changes to the organisation embed
OL,11,Fwell and are not disruptive.
OL,13,F"Practically, it would mean that they
OL,14,Fare applying a little more oversight
OL,15,Fresource, more of the team, more of
OL,16,Ftheir time, to assess and monitor."
