OL,6,FPorts of Jersey added: "Jersey Airport
OL,7,Fcomplies with all aviation regulations
OL,8,Fand safe, secure operations will
OL,9,Falways be our most important priority
OL,10,F... This additional oversight was not
OL,11,Fthe result of an audit, there are no
OL,12,Fgaps in senior management's technical
OL,13,Fknowledge, and there have been no
OL,14,Fchanges to the everyday safe operation
OL,15,Fof the airport."
